patch_description: Band Leader with Band Members.

Original caption: "Commencement exercises, parade on 12th Street." Birds-eye view of graduates and faculty wearing academic robes and mortar boards parading down the center of the street. Rather than single-file, they are walking in rectangular formation like a marching band or military unit. They may be grouped by college. A few scattered spectators stand along the route. Campus buildings and cars are also part of the view.
